<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>د ل ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٨٣٢ - د ل ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أدلفَ يُدلف، إدْلافًا، فهو مُدْلِف، والمفعول مُدْلَف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• أدلف الكِبرُ الشَّيخَ:</span> أقْصَر خَطْوَه وأَثْقل مشيَه <span class="c1">"أدلَفَه الحِمْلُ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>